import React from 'react'
import { Accordion, ActionIcon, Center } from '@mantine/core';
import { IconDots } from '@tabler/icons-react';

const Receipts = () => {
  return (
    <Accordion chevron={null}>
      <Accordion.Item value="apple">
        <Accordion.Control>Apple</Accordion.Control>
        <Accordion.Panel>
          <Accordion chevron={null}>
            <Accordion.Item value="test">
              <Accordion.Control>Test</Accordion.Control>
              <Accordion.Panel>
              <Accordion chevron={null}>
            <Accordion.Item value="test">
              <Accordion.Control>Test-2</Accordion.Control>
              <Accordion.Panel>
                Content
              </Accordion.Panel>
            </Accordion.Item>
          </Accordion>s
              </Accordion.Panel>
            </Accordion.Item>
          </Accordion>
        </Accordion.Panel>
      </Accordion.Item>
    </Accordion>
  )
}

export default Receipts
